## Version

### [GET /api/version](../server/src/api/version.js#L24)

Retrieve version information about the running server.

Example response
```json
{
  "gitHash": "53d77b31f13d0e597da07a9a25aada5bc866118f",
  "gitBranch": "develop"
}
```
